18namespace webrtc {
19
20EncodedImageBuffer::EncodedImageBuffer(size_t size) : size_(size) {
21 buffer_ = static_cast<uint8_t*>(malloc(size));
22}
23
24EncodedImageBuffer::EncodedImageBuffer(const uint8_t* data, size_t size)
25 : EncodedImageBuffer(size) {
26 memcpy(buffer_, data, size);
27}
28
29EncodedImageBuffer::~EncodedImageBuffer() {
30 free(buffer_);
31}
32
33// static
34rtc::scoped_refptr<EncodedImageBuffer> EncodedImageBuffer::Create(size_t size) {
35 return rtc::make_ref_counted<EncodedImageBuffer>(size);
36}
37// static
38rtc::scoped_refptr<EncodedImageBuffer> EncodedImageBuffer::Create(
39 const uint8_t* data,
40 size_t size) {
41 return rtc::make_ref_counted<EncodedImageBuffer>(data, size);
42}
43
44const uint8_t* EncodedImageBuffer::data() const {
45 return buffer_;
46}
47uint8_t* EncodedImageBuffer::data() {
48 return buffer_;
49}
50size_t EncodedImageBuffer::size() const {
51 return size_;
52}
53
54void EncodedImageBuffer::Realloc(size_t size) {
55 // Calling realloc with size == 0 is equivalent to free, and returns nullptr.
56 // Which is confusing on systems where malloc(0) doesn't return a nullptr.
57 // More specifically, it breaks expectations of
58 // VCMSessionInfo::UpdateDataPointers.
59 RTC_DCHECK(size > 0);
60 buffer_ = static_cast<uint8_t*>(realloc(buffer_, size));
61 size_ = size;
62}

74void EncodedImage::SetEncodeTime(int64_t encode_start_ms,
75 int64_t encode_finish_ms) {
76 timing_.encode_start_ms = encode_start_ms;
77 timing_.encode_finish_ms = encode_finish_ms;
78}
79
80absl::optional<size_t> EncodedImage::SpatialLayerFrameSize(
81 int spatial_index) const {
82 RTC_DCHECK_GE(spatial_index, 0);
83 RTC_DCHECK_LE(spatial_index, spatial_index_.value_or(0));
84
85 auto it = spatial_layer_frame_size_bytes_.find(spatial_index);
86 if (it == spatial_layer_frame_size_bytes_.end()) {
87 return absl::nullopt;
88 }
89
90 return it->second;
91}
92
93void EncodedImage::SetSpatialLayerFrameSize(int spatial_index,
94 size_t size_bytes) {
95 RTC_DCHECK_GE(spatial_index, 0);
96 RTC_DCHECK_LE(spatial_index, spatial_index_.value_or(0));
97 RTC_DCHECK_GE(size_bytes, 0);
98 spatial_layer_frame_size_bytes_[spatial_index] = size_bytes;
99}
